<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="62">These are new records to Zhejiang, Hunan, Hubei, Anhui, Sichuan and Guangxi. Most specimens from Jizushan and Hutiaoxia of Central Yunnan have the subapical fascia of elytra reduced to a spot (Fig. 36). The species is distinctive by its coloration and body size.</paragraph>
